#CircuitBreakerSG D-22
Who like Chilli Crab? I'm sure most Singaporeans do. I'm not a "crabby" person but love dipping Mantou with the sauce. Was suddenly craving for it and made my own Mantou from scratch.

No crab, so we make do with Chilli Prawn with Mantou. #cravingsatisfied

The other 2 dishes are Blanched Baby Kailan & Onion Egg.

Enjoy your dinner too!

@belbuttons Thanks Bel. Using whatever there is at home 🤗
Always fabulous meals Yvonne and that’s a perfect substitute
Such a great idea. Wanna try this 😋
Super chilli crab! And that mantou dip!!! 😍🤤
Great if you could share the recipe .
Oh my dear friend.. Y are u torturing me with all yours yummylicious foods.. Mouth watering 🤤🤤🤤

Thank you for pledging to #StayHomeWithAscott. #CapitaLandHopeFoundation will be making a donation of US$10 to Save The Children and we look forward to more of your #StayHomeWithAscott posts. Stay home, stay safe and cook away!
Wa now you make crave for chilli crabs!! Mai hiam these prawns are also very mouthwatering, dip dip..nom nom!!! 😋😍
Chilli crab is one of my fave things to eat and can never get enough of those buns to go with it 🤤🤤🤤😋😋
Oh wow... home made mantou and that sauce!! I'll be dreaming of this tonight!!💖
Wow, that’s so amazing, homemade mantou and with that sauce, heavenly 👍👍👍
@myfoodiegallerysg Thank you, only have prawns at home 😆
That's very good idea to replace crab with prawn. Looks so yummy 😋😋
